<h1>OpenBitTorrent - An open tracker project</h1>
<p class="bigger">OpenBitTorrent is a bittorrent tracker free for anyone to use. You don't need to register, upload or index a torrent anywhere, all you have to do is to include the OpenBitTorrent tracker URL in your torrent.</p>

<h2>How does it work?</h2>
<p>When you create a torrent file the application will ask you for a tracker address, then simply type in OpenBitTorrents tracker URL:</p>
<p class="boxed">
udp://tracker.openbittorrent.com:6969
</p>

